  "instructions": [
    "In a saucepan, mix ginger root with water chestnuts and coconut milk. Add chopped green onions, lime juice, tahini, and ginger cordial.",
    "Simmer over medium heat until thickened, stirring occasionally to prevent sticking. Season with salt.",
    "Spoon the mixture into individual serving dishes or molds. Chill before serving.",
    "For the crisp topping, combine sesame oil, ginger root, green onions, salt, and a bit of water chestnut juice in a small bowl.",
    "Sprinkle over the cooled custard filling to create an attractive and texturally contrasting finish."
